<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178851>
    bibo:endPage "10" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "1608" ;
    dc:creator "Giaretta, Ariovaldo A.; Costa, Hugo C. M." ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "A redescription of Leptodactylus jolyi Sazima and Bokermann (Anura, Leptodactylidae) and the recognition of a new closely related species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178852>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178856>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178857> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178852>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. General aspect of Leptodactylus sertanejo sp. n (above row) and Leptodactylus jolyi (below); all specimens are adult males. Note the larger size and more robust built of the new species. Leptodactylus sertanejo sp. n. — Above: left, Holotype ZUEC 13657; middle, AAG-UFU 3107; right, AAG-UFU 3108. Leptodactylus jolyi— Below: left, AAG- UFU 4092; middle, AAG-UFU 4093; right, AAG-UFU 4146." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178852/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178856>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Leptodactylus sertanejo sp. n.. Holotype ZUEC 13657. A—Dorsal and B—Lateral views of head. C—Palmar and D—Plantar views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178856/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178857>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Advertisement call of two specimens of Leptodactylus sertanejo sp. n.. A and D—Oscillogram, B and E— Sonogram, and C and F—Power spectrum. A – C—LeptodsertanMG 1 AAGb; 20: 20 h, air 23 ºC, water 24 ºC, 18 / Out / 2004. D – F—LeptodsertanMG 2 AAGb; 19: 05 h, air 24.0 ºC, 28 / Jan / 2004. A – C, a two-pulsed call; D – F, a single-pulsed call. Both unvouchered records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178857/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

